title: MBMBaM 483: Face 2 Face: Beemen
description: We’re taking a sick week and tossing up another live show from our most recent tour: Our maiden voyage to the good city Philadelphia. Unfortunately, we left that city worse off than we found it -- which is to say, covered in Beemen. We assume we will not be invited back.
author: shows@mbmbam.com (Justin McElroy)
